title: the wanderers of NYC #lifescrolling

author: Glink
description:
Life Scrolling - The experience of seeing through many perspectives in one place and time. On this episode, we explore Washington Square Park in New York City, a place where people find refuge from the chaos of the city through movement, meditation, and music. The people that populate this small area come from all over the world, what inspires them and what can we learn about life from their perspective?
